   SOMTC
   Analyze
   A concept is the first step to making a new optical instrument. The
   advanced systems development group studies optical solutions for the
   needs of NASA's next generation of projects. They apply the state of
   the art technology to the challenge, or determine the direction to take
   for discovering new science.
     * Advanced Concepts
     * Adaptive Optics
